PN,31409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782233278
OL,3,CHow to beat the heat as UK faces
OL,4,C'tropical nights'
OL,6,FIf your room is hotter than the air
OL,7,Ftemperature outside, having a fan blow
OL,8,Fthe hot air out of the house can help
OL,9,Fcool the room down.
OL,11,FIf the air is hotter outside, you may
OL,12,Fbe better off closing the windows to
OL,13,Fprevent the warm air getting in, and
OL,14,Fhaving a fan blow cool air directly on
OL,15,Fyou.
OL,17,FIs the hot weather set to continue?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
