FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782233278
OL,3,CHow to beat the heat as UK faces
OL,4,C'tropical nights'
OL,6,FA red weather warning for extreme heat
OL,7,Fcovering an area stretching from
OL,8,FLondon to Swansea and Somerset to
OL,9,FBirmingham was issued by the Met
OL,10,FOffice for 9am on Wednesday to 9pm on
OL,11,FThursday.
OL,13,FThese warnings are reserved for the
OL,14,Fmost severe events, the forecaster
OL,15,Fsaid, meaning this heatwave is
OL,16,Fexpected to bring "severe and
OL,17,Fsignificant impacts" including
OL,18,Fwidespread risks for many, not just
OL,19,Fthose who are normally more vulnerable
OL,20,Fto heat, and even danger to life.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
