PN,31411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782233278
OL,3,CHow to beat the heat as UK faces
OL,4,C'tropical nights'
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FWhy are UK houses so warm in summer?
OL,13,FThere has been a dramatic increase in
OL,14,Fthe number of UK households suffering
OL,15,Ffrom overheating during the summer,
OL,16,Faccording to a study by the University
OL,17,Fof East London (UEL).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782233278
OL,3,CHow to beat the heat as UK faces
OL,4,C'tropical nights'
OL,6,F18% of households recorded overheating
OL,7,Fin 2011, compared to a staggering 80%
OL,8,Fin 2022, reported the study that was
OL,9,Fpublished in April 2025.
OL,11,FThe study was prompted by the 2022
OL,12,Fheatwaves, which saw temperatures
OL,13,Fexceed 40C for the first time on
OL,14,Frecord.
OL,16,FOver half of households experienced
OL,17,Fsleep disruption due to the heat, and
OL,18,Fmore than a third of households
OL,19,Freported daily overheating.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782233278
OL,3,CHow to beat the heat as UK faces
OL,4,C'tropical nights'
OL,6,FThe research also highlighted the
OL,7,Fchanging habits of UK households to
OL,8,Fbeat the heat, with 21% of UK homes
OL,9,Fhaving air conditioning installed,
OL,10,Fcompared to 3% in 2011.
OL,12,F"British homes are designed to retain
OL,13,Fheat, not lose it," said Dr Khosravi,
OL,14,Fwho lead the research.
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782233278
OL,3,CHow to beat the heat as UK faces
OL,4,C'tropical nights'
OL,6,F"Even the most energy-efficient
OL,7,Fbuildings - those rated EPC A and B -
OL,8,Fare twice as likely to overheat
OL,9,Fwithout adequate ventilation according
OL,10,Fto the results. This is not just a
OL,11,Fbuilding design issue; it's a public
OL,12,Fhealth issue, and a behavioural one
OL,13,Ftoo."
OL,15,FThe study also highlighted that
OL,16,Foverheating is not limited to specific
OL,17,Ftypes of housing, although those in
OL,18,Frental properties were twice as likely
OL,19,Fto report regular overheating.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31415
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782233278
OL,3,CHow to beat the heat as UK faces
OL,4,C'tropical nights'
OL,6,F"We're facing a real crisis," said Dr
OL,7,FKhosravi.
OL,9,F"Adapting our buildings is vital - but
OL,10,Fequally, we need to adapt our
OL,11,Fbehaviours and attitudes towards heat.
OL,12,FIn the UK, people often see hot
OL,13,Fweather as something enjoyable. But
OL,14,Fwhen it becomes extreme, it can be
OL,15,Fdeadly."
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@]O]qD@AOUwD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/15
